item.title: Cheesecake Factory Reports Strong Q4 Earnings, Beats Estimates
item.description: The Cheesecake Factory (NASDAQ: CAKE) reported Q4 earnings of $1.23 per share, beating analyst estimates of $1.10. Revenue came in at $923 million, up 8% year-over-year.

item.title: CAKE Stock Surges After Menu Expansion Announcement
item.description: Shares of The Cheesecake Factory rose 4.2% following the company's announcement of 15 new restaurant locations planned for 2026.

item.title: Restaurant Industry Outlook 2026: Analysts Weigh In
item.description: Industry analysts remain bullish on casual dining stocks including CAKE, DRI, and EAT as consumer spending shows resilience despite inflation concerns.
